  "title": "use dev-novel in dev environment",
  "body": "**Summary**\r\n\r\nI really liked the developper experience while using storybook for react-instantsearch. Too bad storybook is sticked to a React environment.\r\n\r\nTo achieve a similar experience, I used https://github.com/algolia/dev-novel (still private to Algolians) which will enable us to test independently the result of every widgets in a much easier way.\r\n\r\nI'll add more use-cases of the widgets with default `SearchParameters` while doing #2193 \r\n\r\n**Result**\r\n\r\n![jun-15-2017 12-39-04](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/893837/27177740-b590bb74-51c7-11e7-8a7a-9b4380a0180c.gif)\r\n",
